You are an expert Next.js 15 UI engineer and interaction designer. Phase 1
is complete — the folder structure, data files, types, and config are all
in place. Your task now is Phase 2: build every core section component with
pixel-perfect UI, smooth animations, and recruiter-optimized content layout.

This is the part recruiters actually see. Every spacing decision, every
